			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Ok, here is the info on how to get these gloves:<BR>
Ingot of the Ardent is located on the 3rd lvl of Befallen,<BR>
not sure where though.  The Icon is at the bottom <BR>
of Everfrost River loc of 2996, -5711. You also need<BR>
1 bar of galvanized platinum.  To get the Galvanized<BR>
plat bar you need to have a High lvl enchanter (34<BR>
at least) to enchant it, then take it to a certain <BR>
NPC in Temple of Solusek Ro and have him turn it<BR>
into a bar of galvanized plat, turn all these in to<BR>
get the Gauntlets, and if anyone posts another message<BR>
on how to get these after this is posted I'm going to <BR>
scream!<BR>
